==Reception==
In Getchu.com, ''Hatsuyuki Sakura'' was 3rd best selling games during the month of its release<ref>http://www.getchu.com/pc/salesranking201202.html</ref> and 29th best selling games in March.<ref>http://www.getchu.com/pc/salesranking201203.html</ref> The game was also Getchu's 7th best selling games for the first half of 2012<ref>http://www.getchu.com/pc/2012-1salesranking.html</ref> and 10th best selling games for 2012.<ref>http://www.getchu.com/pc/salesranking2012.html</ref>

In Getchu.com's 2012 [[Bishoujo Game]] Awards (based on user votes), ''Hatsuyuki Sakura'' won first place in overall, with won first place in Scenarios category and Musics Category, 7th in Movies category, 11th in Graphics category, and 20th in Systems category.<ref>http://www.getchu.com/pc/2012_g_ranking/</ref>

